  "philosophy": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": {
        "zh": "",
        "en": ""
      },
      "paragraphs": {
        "zh": [
          "您好！我是乖兒子\n總是鑽研遊戲、沉迷創作、熱衷各方面挑戰\n喜歡在內心扮演不同角色，從不同角度去思考\n以成為別人貴人的思維，來經營 GoodSon Studio。",
          "隨著觀眾人數增加，除了維持做品牌的初衷\n也盡可能的關注每則留言與私訊\n給觀眾們最大的信任。",
          "越來越多合作廠商的邀約\n我也將以資深玩家的角度出發\n從策略討論、創意腳本、B-roll 質感\n做出貼近玩家真正想看、想感受的內容\n為您的品牌打造客製化方案，給出有影響力的數據。",
          "很高興認識大家\nGoodSon Studio 會持續為您帶來高 CP 值服務"
        ],
        "en": [
          "Hi, I am GoodSon\nI am always studying games, immersed in creation, and eager to take on challenges.\nI like to think from different roles and perspectives, running GoodSon Studio with the mindset of becoming someone valuable to others.",
          "As the audience grows, we keep the original intention of building the brand.\nWe also pay close attention to every comment and private message, giving the audience the strongest sense of trust.",
          "With more brand collaboration invitations, I approach every project from a veteran player perspective.\nFrom strategy discussion, creative scripts, and B-roll texture, we create content players truly want to watch and feel.\nWe build customized solutions for your brand and deliver data with real impact.",
          "It is a pleasure to meet everyone.\nGoodSon Studio will continue delivering high-value service for you."
        ]
      },
      "emphasis_text": {
        "zh": "很高興認識大家\nGoodSon Studio 會持續為您帶來高 CP 值服務",
        "en": "It is a pleasure to meet everyone.\nGoodSon Studio will continue delivering high-value service for you."
      },
      "image_path": "assets/philosophy/philosophy.png",
      "image_alt": {
        "zh": "乖兒子團隊與理念形象照片",
        "en": "GoodSon team and philosophy image"
      }
    }
  ],
